Moonlight crowns the boundless sea.

00:10:08.080 --> 00:10:09.960
Pearls are born of the mermaid's tears.

00:10:10.480 --> 00:10:12.120
This pearl is from the East Sea.

00:10:12.390 --> 00:10:14.390
Such a radiant treasure

00:10:14.390 --> 00:10:16.360
is worthy only of the Princess.

00:10:16.670 --> 00:10:18.840
I wish the Princess eternal radiance,

00:10:19.080 --> 00:10:20.550
glowing like celestial lights.

00:10:20.870 --> 00:10:21.910
Much appreciated.

00:10:23.000 --> 00:10:24.480
This jade is from the Kunlun Mountains.

00:10:24.600 --> 00:10:27.600
A fine craftsman spent a year engraving it.

00:10:28.030 --> 00:10:29.840
I wish Your Highness happiness, peace,

00:10:29.840 --> 00:10:30.680
and good luck.

00:10:32.000 --> 00:10:32.840
Thank you.

00:10:36.080 --> 00:10:38.750
Has the social climber

00:10:38.870 --> 00:10:40.440
come empty‑handed,

00:10:40.440 --> 00:10:41.870
planning to slip away?

00:10:43.630 --> 00:10:44.510
Don't be rude.

00:10:45.150 --> 00:10:46.720
Wanning is my guest.

00:10:46.960 --> 00:10:48.600
Her presence alone brings me joy.

00:10:49.120 --> 00:10:50.870
Nothing else matters.

00:10:51.630 --> 00:10:53.080
Princess, you may not care,

00:10:53.390 --> 00:10:55.150
but she is far too lacking in manners.

00:10:55.750 --> 00:10:56.670
Exactly.

00:10:56.840 --> 00:10:58.550
Common blood, common manners.

00:10:58.720 --> 00:10:59.870
How disgraceful.

00:11:00.790 --> 00:11:02.000
Who says I don't have a gift?

00:11:02.270 --> 00:11:03.110
Hongmei.

00:11:10.870 --> 00:11:13.150
Your gifts are truly precious.

00:11:13.440 --> 00:11:16.120
Though my offering is more accessible,

00:11:16.750 --> 00:11:18.150
the ingredients within the sachet

00:11:18.150 --> 00:11:19.910
were handpicked and mixed with care.

00:11:20.630 --> 00:11:21.750
It helps with sleep,

00:11:21.960 --> 00:11:22.960
enhances appetite,

00:11:23.360 --> 00:11:25.750
and with long-term use,
it has cosmetic benefits.

00:11:27.080 --> 00:11:28.750
Lately, my sleep has been troubled,

00:11:29.030 --> 00:11:30.750
and I've been searching for a cure.

00:11:31.150 --> 00:11:34.030
Wanning's gift is the perfect remedy.

00:11:34.630 --> 00:11:35.960
I am very fond of it.

00:11:36.320 --> 00:11:38.270
Since it is so effective,

00:11:39.150 --> 00:11:41.600
why not share it with all the girls here?

00:11:42.120 --> 00:11:44.840
It'd honor Wanning's thoughtful heart.

00:11:52.080 --> 00:11:53.630
How dare you bring such shabby items

00:11:53.960 --> 00:11:56.200
to offend the Princess?

00:11:57.600 --> 00:11:59.030
With all the physicians out there,

00:11:59.120 --> 00:12:00.720
you come here
to show off your petty skill.

00:12:01.000 --> 00:12:02.910
How amusingly bold.

00:12:03.080 --> 00:12:04.320
I heard your father

00:12:04.320 --> 00:12:06.480
was imprisoned for selling

00:12:06.670 --> 00:12:08.240
forbidden medicines.

00:12:08.320 --> 00:12:10.910
Could it contain that as well?

00:12:11.440 --> 00:12:13.390
The materials in this sachet are ordinary,

00:12:13.390 --> 00:12:14.480
but nothing illegal.

00:12:14.960 --> 00:12:16.440
If you don't like it,

00:12:16.440 --> 00:12:17.440
I'll just take it back.

00:12:19.840 --> 00:12:21.510
Are you expecting us to believe it?

00:12:21.750 --> 00:12:24.150
We'll have to examine them ourselves.

00:12:26.120 --> 00:12:28.670
Xu Wanning, you are a mother now.

00:12:29.120 --> 00:12:30.910
Better stay home and nurse your child

00:12:31.240 --> 00:12:33.440
instead of clinging to the powerful.

00:12:33.870 --> 00:12:34.840
Don't you realize

00:12:34.840 --> 00:12:36.910
your reputation's in tatters now?

00:12:37.240 --> 00:12:38.390
Soon your son's honor

00:12:38.390 --> 00:12:41.320
will rot with yours if you keep this up.

00:12:47.870 --> 00:12:49.000
Lady Wang,

00:12:50.480 --> 00:12:52.030
you inherited none

00:12:52.030 --> 00:12:53.320
of your father's scholarly wisdom,

00:12:53.840 --> 00:12:56.150
but you perfected the skills
of a street gossip,

00:12:56.750 --> 00:12:58.080
spouting nonsense all day.

00:12:58.120 --> 00:12:59.000
Your tongue

00:12:59.390 --> 00:13:00.790
must be as long as your girdle by now.

00:13:01.600 --> 00:13:02.960
Although you are a legitimate daughter,

00:13:02.960 --> 00:13:04.240
you are not favored by your father.

00:13:04.670 --> 00:13:06.870
You're nothing but a gossiping fool.

00:13:07.150 --> 00:13:08.360
I advise you

00:13:08.480 --> 00:13:10.150
to go back and read more books.

00:13:10.270 --> 00:13:11.960
How about greasing up your tongue?

00:13:12.550 --> 00:13:14.630
Otherwise, when it gets all tangled up later,

00:13:14.630 --> 00:13:15.790
you'll be even more detested.

00:13:19.790 --> 00:13:20.790
Lady Li,

00:13:21.360 --> 00:13:23.030
so you found your tongue today.

00:13:23.360 --> 00:13:24.630
I heard you're

00:13:24.630 --> 00:13:26.290
a timid mute at home,

00:13:27.080 --> 00:13:28.360
always bowing and cringing.

00:13:28.510 --> 00:13:30.480
